{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0a31d86bc0","title":"傅崇碧传达周恩来的紧急指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1a0afcf964","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":3,"articleId":"0a31d86bc0","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李震","id":"155c01ead4","type":"人物"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"傅崇碧","id":"5ac4b0fa8d","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"5999daa9c2","name":"傅崇碧"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"300807cf94","type":"title","text":"傅崇碧传达周恩来的紧急指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a31d86bc0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0604ebb9cf","type":"paragraph","text":"〖参加单位：政法公社、矿院东方红、北京九中、市局干警等。中央公安部李震副部长亦在场。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a31d86bc0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6861b0664","type":"paragraph","text":"傅崇碧同志传达了周总理如下指示：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a31d86bc0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba210d5837","type":"paragraph","text":"总理派我们来。矿院东方红和政法公社都是左派组织，出现了分歧。北京市公安局是我们的治安中心。在这里不能武斗，双方可派代表进行谈判，每方派十人，到人民大会堂，其它可以这里等待，但不许武斗，在这里也不许互相骂，骂就不好了，暂时不要在这里广播宣传了。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a31d86bc0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"213825bada","type":"paragraph","text":"双方不要派太多的代表，太多了就不好谈了。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a31d86bc0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5d793a5e2","type":"paragraph","text":"在公安局吵起来打起来，敌人会高兴的。而革命同志一点也不会高兴，这样闹下去影响非常坏。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a31d86bc0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2e0f3b8cd","type":"paragraph","text":"谁武斗谁就犯法，我们每个革命造反派都要响应伟大领袖毛主席的“坚持文斗反对武斗”的伟大号召，有问题双方派代表协商解决。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a31d86bc0","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}